# Git Guru Skill

## Commit Style
- **Feat:** New CFD model or solver feature
- **Fix:** Bug fix in code or math formula
- **Docs:** Documentation or daily learning content update
- **Style:** Formatting checks (e.g. Bilingual headers)
- **Refactor:** Code restructuring without behavior change

## Rules
- Messages must be < 50 chars for subject
- Use imperative mood ("Add" not "Added")
